{
  "stem": "17426.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 85.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They just picked one, one, and one, and one, and one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was supposed to be a sort of a reminder that they deal with people in a tough manner, that anyone who has any idea to resist or go any other way or think any other way would end up at the gallows.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the whole city was supposed-- was kept cruising around this circle, where these 10 people hung for hours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this, this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] done by the first army people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't SS men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just army people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember any one of them, because they moved on subsequently and others came, an other gendarmerie came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then at that point, they had a [GERMAN] so-called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what we would call here a administrator of the area, a German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have his name in the book, but I don't remember his name at this point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It escape me, it's been so many years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the administrator of the Dobra region.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He then took over all of the laws and the proclamations and the directives to Jews that they should give up the radios, they should give up any valuables that they had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and all of those things.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Resettlements, driving out from, from your home and bringing into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of this was under this particular [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were driven out our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sent across the street to a school, which wasn't operated, into the attic, in one room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our-- our home, our land, our belonging, we could only take what we could take in our two hands, in our front of our chest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I took some books.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
